NOMA application information

   *NO NEW STUDENTS WILL BE ACCEPTED TO THESE PROGRAMMES*

   Please note that each programme has a different model and different eligibility criteria. Some of the programmes are given as a sandwich programmes where as other programmes are given only at
   the Universities in the South (Africa or Asia). It is important that the candidates read the information carefully and follow the eligibility criteria specially the criteria related to the
   eligibility of countries and University/Institutions.

