   DOWNLOAD: APPLICATION FORM

   Please note that candidates should send applications directly to NTNU. Please do not send the copy of the application to the Norwegian Embassy in your home country or to SIU.

   All enquiries regarding the application procedures should be directed to NTNU's adviser for the NOMA programme.

   Please note that SIU is not responsible for applications and cannot provide information about the status of an application.
